H0.text: What is a nattatorium better known as. Swimming Pool

H1.text: What is a nattatorium better known as. Aquatic Center

H2.text: What is a nattatorium better known as. Indoor Pool

H3.text: What is a nattatorium better known as. Spa pool

A4.text: Once known as 'natatoriums', indoor pools are located inside a building with a roof and are insulated by at least three walls.

A5.text: If a pool is in a separate building, the building may be called a natatorium.
